706060f-a.title: Brooklyn: Noble Street - Franklin Street
706060f-a.text:
106-112 Noble Street, south side, between Franklin Street (right), and
Lorimer Street, showing two Synagogues, from left to right, Beth El at No.
110 and Ahawath Israel of Greenpoint at No. 108. No. 106 is at the extreme
right.
September 1, 1936.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
